data.description: Beautifully Renovated Camelot Tri-Level Home with a Main Floor Family Room Addition in the Highly Desirable H-F School District! This home features a seamless flow between the living room, dining room, and kitchen, adorned with gleaming hardwood floors. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with sleek granite countertops and modern stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with its private bath.    Step outside to a spacious deck overlooking the expansive yard, perfect for quality family time and entertaining. Conveniently located close to H-F Schools, shopping options, easy access to I-80, and the Metra station, making this home an ideal choice for your family's needs.
